				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi folks, I'm hosting a Raid on July 11th to take this guy down and was wondering if any of you could provide answers to some questions I have concerning him.
<br />

<br />
1.  For the spider groups do I need three or four Enchanter groups and should I put more then one enchanter in each group.
<br />

<br />
2.  Can Manaetic be mana drained by Enchanters?
<br />

<br />
3.  If Clerics and healers have a extended range item can they heal outside of Manaetic's AE Range.  And where exactly do they need to stand
<br />

<br />
4.  Does anyone know of a map or layout on the web of the Area the raid takes place.
<br />

<br />
5.  Does either Manetic or the Spiders Summon
<br />

<br />
6.  Is there a limit to the number of flags that can be obtained after he is killed, or are you limited to the 72 person raid limit, and can other groups be rotated in afterwards.
<br />

<br />
7.  Can Spiders be rooted, or even Charmed.
<br />

<br />
8.  What would be a better MT for this guy a SK or a Pally?
<br />

<br />
9.  Any idea on the total number of HP's and how is Manaetics resists.  Would we be better off casting Magic, Poison, Cold, or Fire spells.
<br />

<br />
I'll probably think of others but thanks for any help anyone can offer, some of these may sound like stupid questions but I would rather go in knowing everything I can about him before I get 70 plus people killed in the attempt.
<br />

<br />
Tinker
<br />
Drunks of Tunare</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
