<br />

<br />
You need 2 groups to CC during the fight, 1 for each side.  Or you can go with 4 groups to CC, 1 for each corner.  Anything being fought/killed when he spawns needs to be killed so noone pulls agro into the room.  Clerics/nukers need to heal and nuke from inside the room and they need to make sure they don't overagro.  If one of the bugs gets into the room he blows up and its a 4k AE.
<br />

<br />
Stick him in a corner, move the rest of your raid in and unload on him.  Make sure noone nukes from the doors, if they pull agro he may bug and warp all over (no clue if this is fixed or not, but you don't want him near the doors anyways.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
