			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'd just like to add that the second place MB raids fail is killing the gnome after they've won.  You will have a LOT of spiders mezzed that will all start breaking and agroing all over the place.  Unless you've done exceptionally well in killing the MB, tell your CC teams to just die/FD/whatever to drop agro.  It will save a LOT of pain.  Rez them and have them hail the gnome - he stays up a good 30 minutes unless someone gets him killed.
<br />

<br />
Dd</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
