			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">spiders continually spawn over and over, the only reason there aren't a ton there is because they usually blow up when they enter the Manaetic Behemoths room.  I suggest going and having a look at the area.
<br />

<br />
If you go with mes your enchanter(s) will be holding down quite a few spiders at the end.
<br />

<br />
Spiders only cast the 4000 damage AE when they enter the room, thats why its essential to keep them out.
<br />

<br />
And you simply do not enter the room except to kill the Behemoth and then you get out, during the fight you hope your enchanters did their jobs.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
